(55) “member”, in relation to a company, means— 
(i) the subscriber to the memorandum of the company who shall be deemed to have agreed to become memberof the company, and on its registration, shall be entered as member in its register of members; 
(ii) every other person who agrees in writing to become a member of the company and whose name is entered in the register of members of the company; 
